# Input

```svelte
{#each  items  as  item  }
  <div>{item}</div>
{/each}

{#each items as item,i}
  <div>{item}</div>
{/each}

{#each items as item ( item.id ) }
  <div>{item}</div>
{/each}

```


# Formatted

```svelte
{#each items as item}
	<div>{item}</div>
{/each}

{#each items as item, i}
	<div>{item}</div>
{/each}

{#each items as item (item.id)}
	<div>{item}</div>
{/each}

```
